      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent peer review of model setup, boundary conditions, and material assignments by analyst not involved in original model construction.",
      "rationale": "Each of the three FEA implementations underwent independent peer review by a second qualified analyst. Boundary condition application, material property assignment, and contact definition were verified against the V&V plan. No discrepancies identified. Gradation 2 achieved."
