      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties sourced from batch-specific mechanical testing. Geometric inputs derived from CMM measurements of production hardware. Friction coefficients from published literature with sensitivity analysis.",
      "rationale": "Elastic modulus, yield strength, and tangent modulus for Ti-6Al-4V and UHMWPE determined from batch-specific tensile testing. Screw and rod geometry verified by CMM against CAD nominal. Friction coefficient (μ=0.2 for Ti-Ti, μ=0.1 for Ti-UHMWPE) from published tribology literature; sensitivity analysis shows QoI variation < 3% across μ ± 50%. Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
