      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Testing conducted at multiple loading rates or environmental conditions representative of the COU envelope.",
      "rationale": "Testing conducted at a single quasi-static loading rate (5 mm/min) per ASTM F1717. No variation in loading rate, temperature, or simulated body fluid environment was explored. This factor falls below the required Gradation 3 level; the gap is accepted because the COU is limited to quasi-static structural performance and dynamic loading is outside the intended use. Gradation 2 achieved against required Gradation 3."
    },
    {
