      "rationale": "E/uval computed per ASME V&V 40 Section 5.3 accounting for experimental measurement uncertainty (load cell ±0.5%, displacement ±0.1 mm) and FEA numerical uncertainty. E/uval: stiffness 0.87, yield force 1.14, force at 40 mm 0.76. All percent differences < 10%. Both acceptance criteria satisfied across all three QoIs and all 11 constructs. Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
    {
